Making your Slides FAIR (Findable, Accessible, Interoperable, Reusable)

To do this navigate to your GitHub page and create your first repository;

Name this yourGitHubusername.github.io;

There are many ways to host your render Quarto into html, we will do this locally and deploy our page to GitHub through the branch option.

Your slides will then be public and findable under https://yourGitHubusername.github.io/NameofRepository
